 "body": "The JsonType definition was too restrictive, requiring Mapping values to also be JsonType. This caused mypy to reject valid JSON-like dicts such as dict[str, Collection[str]] or dict[str, object]. Changed to Mapping[str, Any] to match actual JSON behavior.\n\nFixes #7443",
 "created_at": "2026-07-07T12:53:28Z",
